data.description: Welcome to 2304 Strathmore. This charming three-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home offers a recently remodeled kitchen with modern appliances and stylish finishes. Fresh paint, along with new carpet and laminate flooring on the first floor, create a bright and welcoming ambiance. It's currently unoccupied, non-homestead, and holds a rental license. Outside, a fully fenced backyard, deck, and front porch add to the appeal. A two-car detached garage provides convenient parking and extra storage. Nestled in Greencroft neighborhood, it's near parks, schools, shopping, and transportation—a hub for daily living and recreation.
